Package: gha
Title: Useful functions for GitHub Actions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hadley", "Wickham", , "hadley@rstudio.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("RStudio", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: When running code on GitHub actions, you want to make your
    code as easy as possible to debug if something goes wrong. This
    package provides you with tools to achieve that goal.
